1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 17 =

20
00:01:42,500 --> 00:01:43,180
Your Majesty.

21
00:01:45,970 --> 00:01:48,010
Your Majesty. Have some tea.

22
00:02:02,570 --> 00:02:03,660
Are they new proposals?

23
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:05,300
They aren’t.

24
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:07,860
I found these written in Flying White Seal Script

25
00:02:07,860 --> 00:02:09,300
when cleaning up the outer chamber.

26
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:11,460
They didn’t seem to be your handwriting.

27
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:13,060
I racked my brain

28
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:14,540
but was still clueless

29
00:02:14,850 --> 00:02:16,460
until Huan reminded me

30
00:02:17,370 --> 00:02:18,420
that Her Highness

31
00:02:18,420 --> 00:02:19,980
brought these here for comment

32
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:22,540
before the earthquake that day.

33
00:02:24,820 --> 00:02:25,650
Show them to me.

34
00:02:44,970 --> 00:02:46,660
Her Highness does fancy this script.

35
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:50,300
Is she pandering to Your Majesty’s preference?

36
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:53,060
Huan also said

37
00:02:53,820 --> 00:02:56,180
whenever Her Highness was happy or sad,

38
00:02:56,620 --> 00:02:58,740
she’d write in that script.

39
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:02,060
She’s having a cold

40
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:03,860
due to the abnormal weather lately,

41
00:03:04,620 --> 00:03:05,900
but continues to write in the study.

42
00:03:41,820 --> 00:03:42,940
His Majesty has arrived.

43
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:57,220
Those ancient dance books

44
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:58,260
are valuable.

45
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,300
Store them well, Instructor.

46
00:04:01,140 --> 00:04:02,860
= Yang Huaimin =
The betrothal gifts are unique

47
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:04,700
and carefully chosen.

48
00:04:05,260 --> 00:04:07,220
You should think it over.

49
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:10,660
Don’t miss out on such a good marriage.

50
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:16,020
Thank you for your concern, Deputy Officer Yang.

51
00:04:42,420 --> 00:04:43,140
Bihan.

52
00:04:48,180 --> 00:04:48,940
Come here.

53
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,300
We need to talk.

54
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:58,020
Practice hard.

55
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,060
Sorry for troubling you.

56
00:05:20,620 --> 00:05:22,180
The physician said I was fine,

57
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:26,820
so I didn’t tell you

58
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:29,540
to spare you worry.

59
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:32,260
Inside this harem,

60
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:34,300
everyone’s action

61
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:35,780
is under my watch.

62
00:05:38,620 --> 00:05:39,940
I should be punished

63
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:41,060
for hiding things from you.

64
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:43,060
Yes.

65
00:05:44,020 --> 00:05:44,980
After you recover,

66
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:47,420
let’s drink together.

67
00:05:48,380 --> 00:05:50,340
Remember to prepare enough Moyao liquor.

68
00:05:53,380 --> 00:05:56,500
There are eight jars buried in the backyard.

69
00:05:58,780 --> 00:06:00,140
I’ll soon be fine.

70
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:02,140
The liquor is enough to get a cow drunk.

71
00:06:07,620 --> 00:06:08,340
Danshu,

72
00:06:09,180 --> 00:06:10,060
a few days ago,

73
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:12,940
I accidentally heard maids

74
00:06:12,940 --> 00:06:14,060
and eunuchs

75
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:15,900
talking about stories popular outside.

76
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:19,740
It’s said an unmarried girl

77
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:23,740
would use old poems

78
00:06:24,020 --> 00:06:26,540
to convey her love to the scholar she admired.

79
00:06:28,780 --> 00:06:30,140
Unmarried girl?

80
00:06:31,980 --> 00:06:33,460
Unmarried girls

81
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,580
can only marry men

82
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:36,780
chosen by their families.

83
00:06:37,220 --> 00:06:38,500
How could they write love letters to others?

84
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:40,700
I said it’s a story.

85
00:06:40,700 --> 00:06:41,820
It’s not real.

86
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:44,500
OK.

87
00:06:47,180 --> 00:06:49,700
Did you hear them saying

88
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:52,580
what poems she wrote

89
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:55,860
to that scholar?

90
00:06:57,860 --> 00:07:00,020
Why would I pay attention to that?

91
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:04,540
But it reminded me

92
00:07:04,540 --> 00:07:06,300
of a story

93
00:07:07,460 --> 00:07:09,500
that a girl from a military family

94
00:07:09,580 --> 00:07:12,380
was betrothed to her father’s superior.

95
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:18,020
She loved someone else?

96
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:23,100
She married him anyway

97
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:26,380
and was loyal to her husband.

98
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:28,980
She was perfect.

99
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:31,020
Back then, her husband

100
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:34,380
was still

101
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:36,540
a bit immature.

102
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,620
Her husband was

103
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:43,020
superior to her father when he was little?

104
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,340
Then he must be a royal family member.

105
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:51,580
Don’t take it seriously.

106
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:52,780
It’s just a story.

107
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,980
This young man learned about

108
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:57,780
some legendary love stories

109
00:07:58,620 --> 00:08:00,340
but he was inexperienced in love.

110
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:03,300
Although he married a perfect wife,

111
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:06,100
he felt something was missing

112
00:08:08,780 --> 00:08:10,020
until one day...

113
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:12,820
He...

114
00:08:31,860 --> 00:08:34,260
What did Huan do wrong this time?

115
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:36,820
Before coming inside,

116
00:08:36,820 --> 00:08:38,660
I saw her

117
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:42,380
writing “Women should be well-mannered.

118
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:44,980
Don’t act like the ignorant

119
00:08:45,460 --> 00:08:47,940
who always talk behind others’ backs”.

120
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:52,940
She is talkative

121
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:54,140
and must’ve said something wrong.

122
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:56,660
You gave her that punishment to discipline her.

123
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:00,740
What exactly did she do wrong?

124
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:07,500
She gossiped about others.

125
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:10,420
It wasn’t anything severe,

126
00:09:10,900 --> 00:09:12,220
so I told her to copy the book

127
00:09:12,460 --> 00:09:13,460
to train her mind.

128
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:15,820
After all, she’s going to get married

129
00:09:16,300 --> 00:09:17,660
and serve the elderly.

130
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:21,060
As a member of the palace,

131
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:22,260
if she has no manners,

132
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:23,940
that’ll affect the royal family’s image.

133
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:26,420
Get married?

134
00:09:27,460 --> 00:09:28,100
She...

135
00:09:28,860 --> 00:09:30,660
isn’t old enough to leave the palace, is she?

136
00:09:33,460 --> 00:09:35,660
I meant to tell you about it.

137
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:39,820
She came to the palace with me

138
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:41,740
and has served me for five years.

139
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:44,820
She isn’t young at age.

140
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:47,420
If I keep her any longer,

141
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:50,420
by the time she leaves, she’ll be too old

142
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:52,020
to marry a good man.

143
00:09:55,580 --> 00:09:56,460
Danshu.

144
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:59,660
What exactly is Huan’s mistake?

145
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:04,900
Don’t you know her?

146
00:10:07,420 --> 00:10:08,820
Actually,

147
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:10,540
she isn’t suitable

148
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:13,380
to live in the palace.

149
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,180
She came with me from the Cao Mansion

150
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:17,980
and is used to our previous relationship.

151
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:21,060
I thought after some time in the palace,

152
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:23,740
she’d change,

153
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,580
but she’s still

154
00:10:25,660 --> 00:10:27,580
as unruly as before.

155
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:29,940
Nobody is perfect.

156
00:10:31,260 --> 00:10:33,260
She is a bit naughty,

157
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:35,940
but in this palace,

158
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:38,980
who’s more loyal to you than her.

159
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:42,060
Manners can be taught

160
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:43,060
bit by bit,

161
00:10:43,060 --> 00:10:44,820
but respect and loyalty

162
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:46,540
can’t be learned or taught.

163
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:49,140
Huan is different from others.

164
00:10:49,420 --> 00:10:50,380
She grew up with you

165
00:10:50,380 --> 00:10:51,900
like a sister.

166
00:10:58,460 --> 00:10:59,740
Her identity is all the more reason...

167
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:04,220
Were it others,

168
00:11:04,820 --> 00:11:06,940
they could be less mannered.

169
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:09,740
But she’s my closest maid.

170
00:11:10,580 --> 00:11:12,500
Everyone is watching her.

171
00:11:13,300 --> 00:11:14,740
If she does something wrong,

172
00:11:15,140 --> 00:11:17,100
it might be copied by others and grow

173
00:11:17,340 --> 00:11:18,140
to be something severer.

174
00:11:18,140 --> 00:11:21,020
Rules and manners again!

175
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:23,340
You only care about those

176
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:24,620
and disregard people’s emotions.

177
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:26,940
Are you turning all members in your palace,

178
00:11:26,940 --> 00:11:27,900
or the entire harem,

179
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:29,540
into emotionless walking sticks

180
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:30,780
or puppets

181
00:11:30,780 --> 00:11:32,180
for your so-called rules?

182
00:11:42,060 --> 00:11:43,540
Forget about the richest salt merchant

183
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:44,860
or some talented scholar!

184
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:45,900
I want neither of them!

185
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:47,300
If I can’t marry His Majesty,

186
00:11:48,260 --> 00:11:50,100
I’d rather be a nun.

187
00:11:50,700 --> 00:11:52,140
I won’t marry anyone else.

188
00:11:53,380 --> 00:11:56,100
Enough. Be quiet.

189
00:11:57,500 --> 00:12:00,020
Have you no shame?

190
00:12:00,140 --> 00:12:01,820
Stop saying who you want to marry.

191
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:02,700
Besides...

192
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:03,940
I don’t care about shame or whatnot.

193
00:12:05,380 --> 00:12:07,060
All I know is that my heart already belongs to him.

194
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,340
I picked him myself.

195
00:12:08,980 --> 00:12:10,780
He’s the love of my life.

196
00:12:17,020 --> 00:12:18,260
Enjoy the food.

197
00:12:22,740 --> 00:12:23,580
You too.

198
00:12:38,620 --> 00:12:40,220
Can you ask them to leave?

199
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:44,940
You may leave.

200
00:13:03,980 --> 00:13:04,900
You know what?

201
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:07,820
Sitting in your palace,

202
00:13:08,460 --> 00:13:09,940
even when I move my fingers,

203
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:12,260
I’ll fear if I move too much,

204
00:13:12,260 --> 00:13:14,220
too little or in the wrong direction,

205
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:15,860
then you’ll act

206
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:17,300
like your teacher Fan Zhongyan

207
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:20,380
and give me a lecture overloaded with quotes.

208
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:24,060
I feel as if when I was young, I...

209
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:38,460
You must be joking.

210
00:13:41,140 --> 00:13:41,860
I...

211
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:50,780
I always look up to you.

212
00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:00,820
The Caos are a family of soldiers.

213
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:03,980
I’m the only girl

214
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:05,060
in the family.

215
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:07,540
When I was little,

216
00:14:07,540 --> 00:14:08,660
I started to ride and shoot with my brothers.

217
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:12,020
I’m not well-mannered at all.

218
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:14,900
Compared with you,

219
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,140
I’m only a peasant.

220
00:14:18,540 --> 00:14:19,700
All I can do

221
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:21,700
is to look up to you.

222
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:22,660
How could I...

223
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:31,260
If I made you uncomfortable,

224
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:35,020
I should be punished.

225
00:14:47,980 --> 00:14:49,620
Please punish me.

226
00:14:50,060 --> 00:14:50,700
You...

227
00:14:52,460 --> 00:14:53,860
What are you doing?

228
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:56,140
I’m not blaming you.

229
00:14:57,780 --> 00:14:58,660
You aren’t wrong.

230
00:14:58,660 --> 00:14:59,540
You’re just...

231
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:01,660
being too right.

232
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:02,660
I...

233
00:15:11,420 --> 00:15:12,220
I think I know

234
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:14,060
what Huan said that annoyed you.

235
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:16,100
If anyone should be punished,

236
00:15:16,140 --> 00:15:17,940
she isn’t the only one.

237
00:15:18,420 --> 00:15:20,380
I simply want to be a little bit selfish.

238
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:21,820
I do protect those

239
00:15:21,820 --> 00:15:22,700
who truly

240
00:15:22,700 --> 00:15:23,980
care about me.

241
00:15:26,060 --> 00:15:27,300
Maoze and Liaozi

242
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:28,980
will forever be with me.

243
00:15:29,940 --> 00:15:31,060
I have plans

244
00:15:31,060 --> 00:15:32,020
for your maid Huan

245
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:33,300
and Xinhe’s maid Lu Si.

246
00:15:33,820 --> 00:15:35,740
I’m looking for those who are local

247
00:15:35,860 --> 00:15:37,180
and working at the Imperial Hospital
or Imperial Study,

248
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:38,780
to marry them.

249
00:15:39,340 --> 00:15:40,300
Once they get married,

250
00:15:40,300 --> 00:15:41,460
they can still come back

251
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:42,540
to work for you.

252
00:15:52,180 --> 00:15:52,860
Forget about it.

253
00:15:54,740 --> 00:15:56,140
All members in your palace,

254
00:15:57,300 --> 00:15:59,060
more precisely, everyone in the harem,

255
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:01,180
how they should be disciplined,

256
00:16:01,180 --> 00:16:02,260
whether they should stay or leave

257
00:16:02,940 --> 00:16:04,380
are all up to you.

258
00:16:09,180 --> 00:16:10,060
Over the years,

259
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:13,020
you’re flawless

260
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:16,140
as the Empress.

261
00:16:25,660 --> 00:16:27,060
The soup is cold.

262
00:16:29,460 --> 00:16:31,580
I’ll have them reheat it.

263
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:10,180
You didn’t finish your story.

264
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:12,900
That girl from the military family

265
00:17:13,020 --> 00:17:14,620
was loyal and mannered,

266
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:16,420
but her husband found something was missing.

267
00:17:16,980 --> 00:17:17,900
Then what happened?

268
00:17:21,220 --> 00:17:22,340
Did she also

269
00:17:22,340 --> 00:17:23,300
use an old poem

270
00:17:23,740 --> 00:17:25,340
to express her love for her husband?

271
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:29,500
What did she write?

272
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:32,260
Nothing.

273
00:17:32,900 --> 00:17:34,260
She was elegant and well-behaved.

274
00:17:34,820 --> 00:17:35,540
How could she

275
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:37,140
be so frivolous?

276
00:17:57,060 --> 00:17:58,620
Incredible!

277
00:17:58,980 --> 00:18:00,580
Lantiao is amazing.

278
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:02,940
Could you teach me?

279
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:08,300
Unbelievable!

280
00:18:09,180 --> 00:18:10,420
You shameless thief!

281
00:18:18,980 --> 00:18:20,260
What are you doing here again?

282
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:21,860
I didn’t

283
00:18:22,340 --> 00:18:23,700
offend you today.

284
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:27,700
Why are you practicing that?

285
00:18:28,060 --> 00:18:29,540
I’ll perform that dance during the banquet.

286
00:18:29,540 --> 00:18:30,620
You have no chance.

287
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:33,180
Why did you learn it in secret?

288
00:18:35,460 --> 00:18:37,340
You will do that dance,

289
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:38,820
so others can’t?

290
00:18:39,300 --> 00:18:40,660
Who do you think you are?

291
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:45,660
Impressive!

292
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:55,580
I see.

293
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:57,940
You want me

294
00:18:58,500 --> 00:18:59,740
to leave

295
00:19:00,060 --> 00:19:01,700
and try to stab me in the back, don’t you?

296
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:03,460
Even hot soup

297
00:19:03,940 --> 00:19:05,300
couldn’t silence you

298
00:19:05,300 --> 00:19:06,500
and you’re still gossiping around.

299
00:19:06,740 --> 00:19:08,460
Aren’t you afraid your tongue will rot?

300
00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:11,340
You’re crazy!

301
00:19:11,780 --> 00:19:12,380
I... When did I...

302
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:13,140
Shut up.

303
00:19:14,340 --> 00:19:15,700
Stop daydreaming!

304
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:16,940
You’re a thief.

305
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:19,340
You stole my dance and ruined it.

306
00:19:19,780 --> 00:19:20,700
Listen,

307
00:19:22,020 --> 00:19:23,820
I won’t leave this palace

308
00:19:24,020 --> 00:19:25,060
until I die.

309
00:19:27,780 --> 00:19:28,860
Instructor Jia,

310
00:19:29,740 --> 00:19:31,420
please help me.

311
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:33,140
She’s always been a bully.

312
00:19:33,700 --> 00:19:34,900
No one dares to offend her.

313
00:19:35,620 --> 00:19:36,340
But...

314
00:19:36,780 --> 00:19:38,420
But she framed me.

315
00:19:41,420 --> 00:19:42,180
Framed you?

316
00:19:43,620 --> 00:19:44,980
I...I...

317
00:19:45,540 --> 00:19:47,100
I didn’t steal her dance.

318
00:19:47,980 --> 00:19:49,940
Who...who would want to perform it?

319
00:19:50,700 --> 00:19:51,860
You really don’t?

320
00:19:52,620 --> 00:19:53,500
If

321
00:19:54,220 --> 00:19:55,540
she leaves,

322
00:19:56,140 --> 00:19:57,620
you don’t want

323
00:19:58,620 --> 00:19:59,860
to perform her dance

324
00:20:00,420 --> 00:20:01,140
during the banquet

325
00:20:01,140 --> 00:20:02,580
next month?

326
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:13,220
Lantiao,

327
00:20:16,500 --> 00:20:17,900
we all have our own fate.

328
00:20:19,820 --> 00:20:21,620
Some are destined to stand out

329
00:20:22,620 --> 00:20:23,380
and be better than you.

330
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:25,140
Even you’re mad, it won’t change that.

331
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:27,540
People

332
00:20:28,340 --> 00:20:29,980
should seize

333
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:32,220
what comes their way.

334
00:20:37,980 --> 00:20:39,380
You’re a troublemaker.

335
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:42,020
Whenever you’re upset,

336
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:43,180
you’ll lash out.

337
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,300
Keeping you with me

338
00:20:45,940 --> 00:20:47,020
is like

339
00:20:47,220 --> 00:20:48,780
sleeping on a bomb.

340
00:20:50,220 --> 00:20:51,420
Only if you’re gone

341
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:54,820
will I be relieved.

342
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:56,860
I won’t marry other men.

343
00:20:57,820 --> 00:20:59,740
I’ll behave after marrying him.

344
00:20:59,980 --> 00:21:01,140
I’ll serve you

345
00:21:01,140 --> 00:21:02,540
and won’t cause trouble again.

346
00:21:04,100 --> 00:21:05,420
But the one you admire

347
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:07,100
didn’t say he’d marry you.

348
00:21:07,180 --> 00:21:08,260
He loves me.

349
00:21:08,260 --> 00:21:09,820
I’m sure he does.

350
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:13,060
You know that, too, don’t you?

351
00:21:14,020 --> 00:21:16,260
Fine. Even if he does,

352
00:21:16,660 --> 00:21:18,180
that’s only what he says.

353
00:21:19,820 --> 00:21:20,940
Men’s love...

354
00:21:22,580 --> 00:21:24,140
He’s no ordinary man.

355
00:21:24,780 --> 00:21:25,820
Others can’t always

356
00:21:26,180 --> 00:21:26,820
get what they want

357
00:21:26,820 --> 00:21:27,860
no matter how hard they try,

358
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:29,060
but not him.

359
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:29,980
Everything he wants

360
00:21:30,180 --> 00:21:31,260
is within reach.

361
00:21:31,340 --> 00:21:33,020
Besides, I love him, too.

362
00:21:37,780 --> 00:21:38,660
Instructor.

363
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:39,900
Get up.

364
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:40,700
You’re the best.

365
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:42,060
I’m begging you.

366
00:21:42,060 --> 00:21:43,420
Please don’t marry me to others,

367
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:44,660
or I’ll die.

368
00:21:46,580 --> 00:21:47,980
Please, Instructor.

369
00:21:48,940 --> 00:21:49,940
Rise now.

370
00:21:54,820 --> 00:21:55,700
Bihan,

371
00:21:56,300 --> 00:21:57,340
listen,

372
00:21:58,340 --> 00:21:59,900
Mr. Wang

373
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:02,740
is the Elder Princess's nephew-in-law.

374
00:22:04,180 --> 00:22:05,420
Since he saw your dance

375
00:22:05,420 --> 00:22:06,740
at the Princess’ mansion,

376
00:22:06,820 --> 00:22:08,820
he’s set his mind on marrying you.

377
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:11,060
His family

378
00:22:11,340 --> 00:22:12,740
owns a dozen tea houses in the south,

379
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:14,260
as well as four silk stores.

380
00:22:14,420 --> 00:22:15,500
I also heard

381
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:17,580
his father only had him

382
00:22:17,580 --> 00:22:18,580
in his 50s.

383
00:22:18,700 --> 00:22:20,060
His mother is in poor condition.

384
00:22:20,580 --> 00:22:21,580
Once you two get married,

385
00:22:21,740 --> 00:22:22,700
you can take charge of the household.

386
00:22:22,740 --> 00:22:24,220
I won’t do that.

387
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:26,460
I don’t want to be like my eldest aunt

388
00:22:26,740 --> 00:22:27,980
who ages so quickly

389
00:22:27,980 --> 00:22:28,940
and is unlikable,

390
00:22:28,980 --> 00:22:29,980
mean and vulgar.

391
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:30,820
What’s good about that?

392
00:22:31,900 --> 00:22:33,260
What’s good about that?

393
00:22:34,580 --> 00:22:35,500
She was the one

394
00:22:35,700 --> 00:22:36,900
who told your uncle

395
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:38,180
not to take you and your mother in

396
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:40,060
after your father passed away.

397
00:22:40,780 --> 00:22:41,900
What’s good about that?

398
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:44,020
One day,

399
00:22:44,220 --> 00:22:45,540
I’ll make her kneel

400
00:22:45,540 --> 00:22:46,500
and bow to me.

401
00:22:51,660 --> 00:22:52,540
Ridiculous!

402
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:57,140
In this palace,

403
00:22:57,900 --> 00:22:59,900
even if His Majesty likes you

404
00:22:59,900 --> 00:23:01,060
and makes you his concubine,

405
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:02,380
the one in charge

406
00:23:02,540 --> 00:23:04,460
is still the Empress.

407
00:23:06,020 --> 00:23:06,900
Look,

408
00:23:07,140 --> 00:23:08,900
if he has feelings for you,

409
00:23:08,940 --> 00:23:10,220
why hasn’t he summoned you again

410
00:23:10,340 --> 00:23:11,900
since last time?

411
00:23:12,100 --> 00:23:13,420
Why you had to leave

412
00:23:13,420 --> 00:23:14,820
right after the Empress came that day?

413
00:23:19,540 --> 00:23:20,540
Think about it.

414
00:23:25,940 --> 00:23:27,060
Bihan,

415
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,020
take my advice.

416
00:23:29,940 --> 00:23:30,820
Be good.

417
00:23:31,900 --> 00:23:33,340
Marrying a capable man

418
00:23:33,460 --> 00:23:34,340
who has properties

419
00:23:34,340 --> 00:23:36,060
and can let you take charge of the house

420
00:23:36,380 --> 00:23:37,660
is more practical.

421
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:38,780
Understand?

422
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:43,500
Your so-called love

423
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:44,940
is useless.

424
00:23:45,740 --> 00:23:46,900
A case of gold

425
00:23:46,900 --> 00:23:48,260
and a mansion are more valuable.

426
00:23:50,060 --> 00:23:51,580
Think carefully about what I said.

427
00:24:14,300 --> 00:24:15,700
His Majesty has left.

428
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:18,020
Miss,

429
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:20,580
he told you to stay indoors before leaving

430
00:24:21,900 --> 00:24:22,860
to keep you warm

431
00:24:23,020 --> 00:24:24,220
so that your condition wouldn’t worsen.

432
00:24:25,260 --> 00:24:26,460
After all, he especially

433
00:24:26,660 --> 00:24:27,980
brought you the medicine.

434
00:24:56,220 --> 00:24:56,900
Miss.

435
00:25:12,700 --> 00:25:14,980
I’ll be out of the palace soon.

436
00:25:15,940 --> 00:25:17,340
May I still call you like this?

437
00:25:18,660 --> 00:25:20,340
Anyway, you never meant

438
00:25:21,420 --> 00:25:22,900
to drive me out then.

439
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:24,740
This rule was only made as an excuse.

440
00:25:26,180 --> 00:25:27,820
I’ll ask mother to come tomorrow

441
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:29,860
to make preparations.

442
00:25:31,340 --> 00:25:33,460
You can leave with her in a few days.

443
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:37,540
Although you broke the rule and have to leave,

444
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:40,620
it’s not a serious offense.

445
00:25:41,820 --> 00:25:43,260
You’re simply too outgoing

446
00:25:43,460 --> 00:25:44,900
to be in the palace.

447
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:18,660
Mother always likes you.

448
00:26:20,820 --> 00:26:21,900
When you get back,

449
00:26:23,020 --> 00:26:24,460
she’ll treat you well.

450
00:26:24,740 --> 00:26:26,060
She’ll prepare enough dowries for you

451
00:26:27,740 --> 00:26:30,100
and find you a good husband.

452
00:26:34,980 --> 00:26:36,500
You’re capable and smart,

453
00:26:36,620 --> 00:26:37,700
passionate and kind.

454
00:26:38,940 --> 00:26:39,820
After you leave,

455
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:42,180
you should be a good wife and mother,

456
00:26:44,540 --> 00:26:45,980
have children

457
00:26:47,300 --> 00:26:48,260
and grandchildren.

458
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:53,460
I understand

459
00:26:54,180 --> 00:26:55,780
you’re doing this for my sake,

460
00:26:57,700 --> 00:26:59,980
but I only want to spend time

461
00:27:00,860 --> 00:27:02,380
with the people I like.

462
00:27:03,180 --> 00:27:04,540
I don’t want to have children

463
00:27:06,020 --> 00:27:06,900
or grandchildren

464
00:27:07,340 --> 00:27:08,180
with some stranger.

465
00:27:11,220 --> 00:27:11,900
Master,

466
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:15,540
it’s my fault.

467
00:27:17,260 --> 00:27:18,940
I’d rather die

468
00:27:19,500 --> 00:27:20,500
than...

469
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:24,180
than...

470
00:27:24,460 --> 00:27:26,180
ruin her reputation.

471
00:27:27,740 --> 00:27:28,620
Reputation?

472
00:27:30,820 --> 00:27:32,140
All that you’ve done

473
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,900
has already impaired it.

474
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:44,620
Dismissing her from her post

475
00:27:45,140 --> 00:27:47,500
and asking her to leave

476
00:27:49,420 --> 00:27:50,820
on the pretext of being willful, impetuous

477
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:52,300
and unable to serve the Empress well

478
00:27:54,060 --> 00:27:56,580
is the best way to protect her.

479
00:28:02,100 --> 00:28:03,620
Her Highness was decisive

480
00:28:04,140 --> 00:28:06,060
and made the best decision.

481
00:28:06,900 --> 00:28:08,420
This way, you’re safe, too.

482
00:28:11,220 --> 00:28:13,420
She was Her Highness's closest maid.

483
00:28:15,020 --> 00:28:16,340
His Majesty planned

484
00:28:16,620 --> 00:28:17,900
to marry her to a good man

485
00:28:19,380 --> 00:28:20,820
once she is old enough.

486
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:22,740
Master,

487
00:28:23,500 --> 00:28:25,180
I’m willing to take her punishment.

488
00:28:25,180 --> 00:28:27,580
If you don’t want to make things worse,

489
00:28:29,340 --> 00:28:30,420
don’t even think about

490
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,820
giving up your life.

491
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:36,300
If you kill yourself,

492
00:28:37,260 --> 00:28:38,500
she’ll have to die

493
00:28:38,820 --> 00:28:41,140
for fornicating with a eunuch.

494
00:28:45,180 --> 00:28:47,260
You’re too obsessed.

495
00:28:50,700 --> 00:28:52,060
Within these walls,

496
00:28:52,820 --> 00:28:53,940
behind the closed gate,

497
00:28:56,020 --> 00:28:57,180
you’re loyal to me

498
00:28:57,180 --> 00:28:58,900
and won’t fall in love with His Majesty.

499
00:29:03,420 --> 00:29:05,820
But you shouldn’t have loved the wrong person.

500
00:29:08,540 --> 00:29:09,660
Once you’re out,

501
00:29:10,980 --> 00:29:12,900
you can marry a perfect young man.

502
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:14,820
You two will love each other

503
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:15,980
and enjoy a happy marriage.

504
00:29:16,660 --> 00:29:17,820
Then you’ll realize

505
00:29:17,860 --> 00:29:18,900
how silly you sound now.

506
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:21,900
But back in our mansion,

507
00:29:22,380 --> 00:29:25,100
when servants flattered me

508
00:29:25,420 --> 00:29:26,220
and said they liked me,

509
00:29:26,260 --> 00:29:27,660
I spat at them immediately

510
00:29:27,660 --> 00:29:28,580
and warned them

511
00:29:28,660 --> 00:29:30,500
that if they didn’t stop, I’d report them.

512
00:29:37,700 --> 00:29:38,740
All these years,

513
00:29:40,300 --> 00:29:41,820
you are all I have,

514
00:29:44,020 --> 00:29:46,020
especially in this palace.

515
00:29:47,980 --> 00:29:48,860
As for him,

516
00:29:49,580 --> 00:29:50,980
His Majesty is his world.

517
00:29:53,140 --> 00:29:54,820
We have so much to talk about.

518
00:29:56,740 --> 00:29:57,860
And we shared

519
00:29:58,700 --> 00:30:00,300
a few secrets, too.

520
00:30:01,620 --> 00:30:02,660
We both believe

521
00:30:03,420 --> 00:30:04,340
in this world,

522
00:30:04,460 --> 00:30:05,820
only you are good enough

523
00:30:05,820 --> 00:30:06,700
for His Majesty.

524
00:30:07,900 --> 00:30:09,100
And His Majesty

525
00:30:09,340 --> 00:30:10,380
is the only match for you.

526
00:30:12,460 --> 00:30:14,820
When you two had a good time,

527
00:30:15,540 --> 00:30:16,620
we’d be happy for you.

528
00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:20,180
When you two argued,

529
00:30:21,540 --> 00:30:23,660
we’d feel heartbroken.

530
00:30:30,620 --> 00:30:32,460
I don’t know where I should begin

531
00:30:35,060 --> 00:30:36,900
but I love listening to him

532
00:30:38,100 --> 00:30:39,980
even if it’s not about you.

533
00:30:41,940 --> 00:30:43,020
He remembers

534
00:30:43,700 --> 00:30:44,940
what I like.

535
00:30:46,820 --> 00:30:48,980
He knows I love light green

536
00:30:49,740 --> 00:30:51,020
not dark green.

537
00:30:52,780 --> 00:30:54,380
He remembers that cheese

538
00:30:55,580 --> 00:30:56,860
makes me sick,

539
00:30:58,780 --> 00:30:59,620
and

540
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:02,860
my favorite kind of plum blossom.

541
00:31:03,940 --> 00:31:04,740
Enough.

542
00:31:08,220 --> 00:31:10,220
Luckily,

543
00:31:13,420 --> 00:31:14,900
I didn’t change my mind

544
00:31:16,060 --> 00:31:17,140
because I don’t want you to leave

545
00:31:18,540 --> 00:31:20,140
and I wasn’t convinced

546
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:22,860
by His Majesty’s tempting promises

547
00:31:24,020 --> 00:31:25,420
and let you stay.

548
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:29,740
You don’t belong here.

549
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:36,660
Huan,

550
00:31:41,420 --> 00:31:42,540
after you’re out,

551
00:31:43,540 --> 00:31:44,940
you can rest for a while,

552
00:31:46,300 --> 00:31:47,300
read some books

553
00:31:48,340 --> 00:31:50,180
or ride horses with my brothers.

554
00:31:52,140 --> 00:31:53,100
When you leave here,

555
00:31:54,540 --> 00:31:55,820
you’ll see a bigger world

556
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:57,020
and grow a bigger heart.

557
00:31:59,460 --> 00:32:00,860
Then you’ll forget about

558
00:32:00,860 --> 00:32:01,620
all these distractions.

559
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:04,860
But...

560
00:32:06,300 --> 00:32:07,460
But what about you?

561
00:32:14,900 --> 00:32:16,340
Keep it in mind

562
00:32:17,420 --> 00:32:19,100
that you lost control of yourselves

563
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:21,220
and crossed the line,

564
00:32:23,340 --> 00:32:24,420
so you can’t

565
00:32:24,420 --> 00:32:26,020
stay here forever

566
00:32:27,740 --> 00:32:30,380
to be with the ones you love

567
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,660
and care about the most.

568
00:32:37,820 --> 00:32:38,740
Luckily,

569
00:32:39,580 --> 00:32:41,140
Her Highness took care of everything.

570
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:44,140
If you don’t stop,

571
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:46,740
or take one more step,

572
00:32:49,540 --> 00:32:51,740
your love of life

573
00:32:52,700 --> 00:32:54,100
will fall into the abyss

574
00:32:54,580 --> 00:32:56,300
and be smashed into pieces.

575
00:33:03,700 --> 00:33:04,420
Master,

576
00:33:06,220 --> 00:33:09,340
we can’t treat ourselves as humans,

577
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:10,700
can we?

578
00:33:11,620 --> 00:33:12,340
No.

579
00:33:14,900 --> 00:33:17,300
We have to remember we’re humans.

580
00:33:20,020 --> 00:33:21,060
That’s why

581
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:22,740
we must show others

582
00:33:23,580 --> 00:33:25,940
what we have in common with them.

583
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:29,460
Do not do things

584
00:33:30,660 --> 00:33:32,100
that we shouldn’t have,

585
00:33:33,780 --> 00:33:35,020
or give promises

586
00:33:35,020 --> 00:33:37,140
that we can’t keep.

587
00:33:39,740 --> 00:33:40,860
Otherwise,

588
00:33:41,860 --> 00:33:43,100
you’ll only expose

589
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:46,980
your weaknesses to them.

590
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:50,900
But...what about love?

591
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:57,780
Love?

592
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:07,740
You should

593
00:34:10,020 --> 00:34:11,500
lock it up

594
00:34:12,900 --> 00:34:14,180
in your heart.

595
00:34:23,540 --> 00:34:24,740
“Gentlemen

596
00:34:29,500 --> 00:34:30,700
are as clear

597
00:34:34,020 --> 00:34:35,180
as crystal”.

598
00:34:36,660 --> 00:34:37,340
Your Majesty.

599
00:34:40,060 --> 00:34:40,940
Maoze?

600
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:43,100
Is something wrong?

601
00:34:46,020 --> 00:34:46,740
Nothing.

602
00:34:47,340 --> 00:34:49,580
Liaozi is having a cold and a fever,

603
00:34:49,740 --> 00:34:51,540
so someone else filled in for him tonight.

604
00:34:51,700 --> 00:34:53,220
I’m here to make sure

605
00:34:53,420 --> 00:34:54,420
if you are taken good care of.

606
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:57,420
You’re here already,

607
00:34:57,820 --> 00:34:59,220
then I’ll keep you for the night.

608
00:34:59,940 --> 00:35:01,020
Tell Mao to go back.

609
00:35:01,020 --> 00:35:02,180
You can take his shift.

610
00:35:02,540 --> 00:35:03,460
All these years,

611
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:05,300
no one is better than you.

612
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:07,980
Have a look.

613
00:35:08,300 --> 00:35:08,940
What do you think?

614
00:35:14,540 --> 00:35:15,380
I know nothing

615
00:35:15,980 --> 00:35:17,300
about the Flying White Seal Script.

616
00:35:18,500 --> 00:35:19,620
You’ve watched me practicing it for years.

617
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:20,820
How come you don’t know anything?

618
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:23,980
It’s a bit strange.

619
00:35:24,940 --> 00:35:25,940
It seems that Her Highness

620
00:35:26,740 --> 00:35:28,260
wrote this poem to Your Majesty,

621
00:35:31,020 --> 00:35:32,340
but the handwriting

622
00:35:32,780 --> 00:35:35,100
isn’t soft at all

623
00:35:35,540 --> 00:35:38,100
but rather fierce and sharp.

624
00:35:38,980 --> 00:35:40,140
Compared with yours,

625
00:35:40,620 --> 00:35:42,460
it lacks a hint of elegance.

626
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:46,820
You’re flattering me, too.

627
00:35:49,380 --> 00:35:50,380
You aren’t alone.

628
00:35:52,940 --> 00:35:54,180
She confuses me as well.

629
00:35:58,780 --> 00:35:59,860
She’s

630
00:35:59,940 --> 00:36:02,180
a thorough and perfect empress

631
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:03,820
who covers herself

632
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:06,220
with rules and manners.

633
00:36:08,020 --> 00:36:09,020
But sometimes,

634
00:36:11,620 --> 00:36:13,620
I feel attached to her

635
00:36:15,100 --> 00:36:16,140
as if

636
00:36:17,060 --> 00:36:18,700
we knew each other long ago.

637
00:36:22,940 --> 00:36:24,060
We’re close

638
00:36:24,780 --> 00:36:26,740
but not like family.

639
00:36:29,420 --> 00:36:31,420
I can’t treat her the same way I treat Xinhe.

640
00:36:32,700 --> 00:36:33,780
Occasionally,

641
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:36,620
she intimidates me.

642
00:36:42,140 --> 00:36:43,020
Perhaps...

643
00:36:44,580 --> 00:36:46,620
she and the Empress Dowager are indeed alike.

644
00:36:50,260 --> 00:36:51,660
With all due respect,

645
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:53,740
she doesn’t have one-tenth

646
00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:54,860
of Empress Zhangxian’s toughness.

647
00:36:55,420 --> 00:36:57,620
She cares about your feelings.

648
00:36:58,300 --> 00:36:59,180
In that sense,

649
00:36:59,180 --> 00:36:59,980
she isn’t

650
00:37:00,020 --> 00:37:02,060
too different from

651
00:37:02,140 --> 00:37:03,500
other jealous concubines.

652
00:37:04,700 --> 00:37:05,540
The only difference is

653
00:37:05,780 --> 00:37:07,660
that others cry,

654
00:37:07,660 --> 00:37:08,860
get angry and argue with others

655
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:10,620
while Her Highness

656
00:37:10,620 --> 00:37:11,940
throws those so-called rules

657
00:37:11,940 --> 00:37:12,900
at Your Majesty.

658
00:37:13,100 --> 00:37:15,780
They all have their ways to vent their anger.

659
00:37:24,620 --> 00:37:25,820
That’s interesting.

660
00:37:30,100 --> 00:37:32,100
I’m surprised that you know so much

661
00:37:32,100 --> 00:37:33,380
about women

662
00:37:34,340 --> 00:37:35,620
as if you could read Danshu’s mind.

663
00:37:41,380 --> 00:37:42,500
This is Lv Yijian’s proposal.

664
00:37:43,340 --> 00:37:44,940
You know what he said?

665
00:37:47,340 --> 00:37:48,260
Han Qi said

666
00:37:48,700 --> 00:37:51,100
despite Lv Yijian’s alleged corruption,

667
00:37:51,340 --> 00:37:53,020
he is a capable official.

668
00:37:54,100 --> 00:37:54,860
Now,

669
00:37:55,620 --> 00:37:56,580
the west is unstable.

670
00:37:56,980 --> 00:37:58,500
Disasters struck the Capital and the environs.

671
00:37:58,820 --> 00:38:00,180
We should put the past behind

672
00:38:00,740 --> 00:38:02,620
and reinstate Lv Yijian in the Cabinet.

673
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:04,980
Yet Lv Yijian replied

674
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:07,220
that the state needs

675
00:38:07,980 --> 00:38:09,660
an all-round experienced official

676
00:38:09,780 --> 00:38:11,300
who has sound judgment

677
00:38:11,540 --> 00:38:12,900
to pacify the west.

678
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:14,660
Fan Zhongyan

679
00:38:15,020 --> 00:38:16,060
is the best candidate.

680
00:38:19,540 --> 00:38:20,460
This shows

681
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:22,660
gentlemen can rise above their differences.

682
00:38:29,180 --> 00:38:30,900
Bihan is stubborn.

683
00:38:30,980 --> 00:38:32,180
I’m afraid she will...

684
00:38:32,700 --> 00:38:33,780
Can we wait a bit longer?

685
00:38:35,060 --> 00:38:36,220
The world is fickle

686
00:38:36,220 --> 00:38:37,780
and so are people.

687
00:38:38,860 --> 00:38:41,260
However unique, willful

688
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:44,100
or more passionate she is,

689
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,980
compared with state affairs,

690
00:38:45,980 --> 00:38:47,460
she’s less important.

691
00:38:47,980 --> 00:38:49,740
Once the west is in chaos...

692
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:51,460
Chaos?

693
00:38:53,620 --> 00:38:54,620
What do you mean?

694
00:38:55,260 --> 00:38:56,060
Nothing.

695
00:38:57,940 --> 00:38:59,500
Will there be a war?

696
00:39:03,460 --> 00:39:04,980
Say something.

697
00:39:05,580 --> 00:39:06,820
Look,

698
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:10,100
Li Deming’s loyalty was fake.

699
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:12,580
He seemed to be dependent on Song and Liao,

700
00:39:12,940 --> 00:39:15,220
but actually, he restored the economy

701
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:17,060
and attacked Tibet and Uighur.

702
00:39:18,260 --> 00:39:19,580
Over the past years,

703
00:39:19,940 --> 00:39:22,060
he’s occupied the west

704
00:39:22,260 --> 00:39:24,820
and prepared for the revolt.

705
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:26,620
Sadly,

706
00:39:27,260 --> 00:39:29,540
he died too young.

707
00:39:32,220 --> 00:39:33,660
His son Yuanhao

708
00:39:34,140 --> 00:39:36,700
is more rebellious and cunning.

709
00:39:37,420 --> 00:39:39,900
And his father laid a solid foundation for him.

710
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:42,340
Over the past years,

711
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:44,580
he’s been forcing people to shave their heads,

712
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:46,060
promoting their own characters

713
00:39:47,100 --> 00:39:48,820
and absorbing talents

714
00:39:48,820 --> 00:39:50,660
who failed our exam.

715
00:39:51,140 --> 00:39:54,140
He learned from us and established the court

716
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:56,100
and called himself emperor.

717
00:39:59,540 --> 00:40:00,580
A few days ago,

718
00:40:01,060 --> 00:40:02,300
his uncle

719
00:40:02,420 --> 00:40:04,420
attempted to surrender himself to us

720
00:40:04,420 --> 00:40:05,460
but was killed by him.

721
00:40:06,860 --> 00:40:07,900
I guess

722
00:40:09,260 --> 00:40:11,220
he’ll soon

723
00:40:11,660 --> 00:40:14,220
proclaim himself emperor and rebel.

724
00:40:19,940 --> 00:40:20,700
Goodness!

725
00:40:21,100 --> 00:40:22,220
What should we do?

726
00:40:29,700 --> 00:40:31,900
If the war is on,

727
00:40:33,020 --> 00:40:33,820
your...

728
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:37,340
your antiques

729
00:40:37,740 --> 00:40:39,660
won’t be worth too much.

730
00:40:43,660 --> 00:40:44,580
You spent

731
00:40:45,140 --> 00:40:47,300
all your savings

732
00:40:47,540 --> 00:40:49,500
and money others offered you...

733
00:40:49,660 --> 00:40:50,300
on...

734
00:40:50,540 --> 00:40:52,300
on these things.

735
00:40:53,580 --> 00:40:54,340
No.

736
00:40:55,540 --> 00:40:57,020
I have to get some gold.

737
00:40:57,420 --> 00:40:58,540
Gold is more valuable.

738
00:41:00,620 --> 00:41:02,100
Stop laughing! This isn’t the time.

739
00:41:02,100 --> 00:41:03,460
However violent

740
00:41:03,460 --> 00:41:04,700
the Tangut people are,

741
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:07,540
they’ll only rob some silk,

742
00:41:07,540 --> 00:41:08,740
grains, silver and gold.

743
00:41:08,980 --> 00:41:11,180
Our lives won’t be affected.

744
00:41:12,820 --> 00:41:14,140
Even if others lack supplies,

745
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:15,020
with me here,

746
00:41:15,620 --> 00:41:17,260
you have nothing to worry about.

747
00:41:17,540 --> 00:41:18,140
But...

748
00:41:18,140 --> 00:41:20,180
Besides, you still have Bihan.

749
00:41:23,740 --> 00:41:25,780
Whether she will marry the man she likes

750
00:41:25,860 --> 00:41:27,820
or my nephew,

751
00:41:29,060 --> 00:41:32,260
she’ll have to thank you for it.

752
00:41:34,020 --> 00:41:36,380
Both of them

753
00:41:36,380 --> 00:41:38,420
can be your support.

754
00:41:42,620 --> 00:41:44,060
But I still think

755
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:46,100
testing her with her marriage

756
00:41:47,860 --> 00:41:48,780
is inappropriate.

757
00:41:49,540 --> 00:41:51,980
She needs to know herself better.

758
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:54,980
And we can find out

759
00:41:55,860 --> 00:41:57,700
if she’s so obsessed

760
00:41:58,260 --> 00:42:00,260
that she won’t quit

761
00:42:00,740 --> 00:42:02,500
or hesitate no matter what.

762
00:42:06,260 --> 00:42:07,300
If that’s the case,

763
00:42:07,300 --> 00:42:08,420
let’s give her a push.

764
00:42:11,740 --> 00:42:13,660
Anyway, it has to be settled soon.

765
00:42:15,060 --> 00:42:18,060
Once the war breaks out in the west,

766
00:42:18,780 --> 00:42:20,860
or something happens at court,

767
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:27,420
it’ll be much more difficult.

768
00:42:39,180 --> 00:42:48,840
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

769
00:42:50,180 --> 00:42:58,520
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

770
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:06,080
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

771
00:43:07,060 --> 00:43:11,220
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

772
00:43:12,660 --> 00:43:18,140
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

773
00:43:18,140 --> 00:43:22,930
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

774
00:43:26,590 --> 00:43:32,230
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

775
00:43:32,230 --> 00:43:37,140
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

776
00:43:37,640 --> 00:43:43,400
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

777
00:43:43,400 --> 00:43:48,490
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

778
00:43:48,920 --> 00:43:53,850
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

779
00:43:54,470 --> 00:43:59,320
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

780
00:44:00,010 --> 00:44:05,160
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

781
00:44:05,660 --> 00:44:10,700
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

782
00:44:11,240 --> 00:44:15,310
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

783
00:44:16,780 --> 00:44:21,420
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

784
00:44:22,440 --> 00:44:27,600
♪ The howling wind ♪

785
00:44:27,970 --> 00:44:32,040
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

786
00:44:33,520 --> 00:44:38,440
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

787
00:44:39,100 --> 00:44:44,320
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

788
00:44:44,740 --> 00:44:50,020
♪ The howling wind ♪

789
00:44:50,310 --> 00:44:55,210
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

790
